reviews.title: ControllerService lingers on
reviews.comment: Quitting the app still leaves the memory eating ControllerService running in the background. Why can\'t apps just quit everything instead of chewing up RAM and data? Does it matter for a quote system that\'s more than 10min delayed that it constantly refreshes in the background? Fair enough if it was live, but even then it could just periodically refresh while the app was running, not when it\'s closed. Uninstalled.
reviews.author: A Google User
